metadata.name: Block Quest PassKey #1/500
metadata.description:
This Block Quest PassKey allows entry to the token gated "Area 21" of Flagship

Add this NFT in your wallet connected to your Spatial.io account.

Enter Flagship Area-21 at this link 

https://www.spatial.io/s/FLAGSHIP-AREA-21-636f5342a6af410001264fd2?share=4927613140681321342

The first clue is straight forward. 

Overthink or underthink. One of these may be the key to a key!  

Solve the clue, to reveal the location of PassKey#2.

Good Luck.  
etherstu
